documents.content: France (French: [fs] Listen), officially the French Republic (French: Rpublique franaise [epyblik fsz]),[14] is a country located primarily in Western Europe. It also includes overseas regions and territories in the Americas and the Atlantic,Pacific and Indian Oceans,[XII] giving it one of the largest discontiguous exclusive economic zones in the world.
